            <h1>Full of Live Demos</h1>
            <p>The Learn UI Design course is chocked full of <em>live video demos</em>.  Watch as we generate dozens of layouts, elements, color schemes, and more.  From blank canvas to finished design, you'll see how the process looks at every step of the way.</p>
            <p>Articles can have good information, and slide decks can be illustrative – but live videos combine the best of both worlds <em>and then some</em>.  In addition, I've augmented the videos with screenshots of hundreds of the best interfaces for web and mobile.  We'll talk about the very best of what's out there.  But the focus is on opening up Sketch (<a href="#faq-sketch">or Adobe XD or Figma</a>) and <em>doing it for ourselves</em>.</p>
            <p><strong>Think of it this way:</strong> I've designed these videos to be like watching over my shoulder, as I share the tricks, tips, and frameworks that have helped me design UI every day for companies around the world.</p>
            <p>We're going to dive into and break down every major area of interface design.</p>
